==English==
===Noun===
'''pointer''' (''plural'' '''pointers''')

#Anything that [[point]]s or is used for pointing.
#A [[needle]]-like component of a [[timepiece]] or measuring device that indicates the time or the current [[reading]] of the device.
#A breed of hunting dog.
#(''computing'') A [[variable]] that stores the [[address]] of another variable.
#(''computer programming'') An [[icon]] that indicates the position of the [[mouse]].

====Synonyms====
*(''of a timepiece''): [[hand]]
*(''of a measuring device''): [[needle]]
*(''icon''): [[mouse pointer]]

